Family Owned Mexican Restaurant Group Senor Tequila was built on the concept that great Mexican food can be fast and fresh and our customers have loved the fact that they can come in for a speedy, delicious and authentic meal. Senor Tequila has been a staple of Charleston for years and our customers are like family.

Review by - Google

Sara R:
five star review by 
If you go here, you will not leave hungry. Amazing endless chips and salsa they refill very promptly. Service is fast and very nice. There's a pretty solid kids menu too.

Review by - Google

Emma H:
five star review by 
The food and drinks were great! Fast and super friendly service. Best salsa I've had since moving to south Carolina. We will definitely be returning!

Review by - Google

Adam M:
five star review by 
Our 1st visit here while on vacation. They were crazy busy and we were seated right away and the food, excellent! Will definitely come back!

Review by - Google

five star review by 
We were in town and got a to go order. When I got there to pick it up there were people everywhere. It was a great atmosphere! Next time we'll dine in. Our food was great as well.
